snippet.title: Kemco RPG Selection Vol. 7 Trailer | For PS4 Launches July 15 in Japan
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more game trailers 👉 http://bit.ly/mustachegamer

Kemco RPG Selection Vol. 7 will launch for PlayStation 4 on July 15 in Japan for 4,280 yen, publisher Kemco announced.
